column16: Dustin Ackley pops out to third baseman Alberto Callaspo in foul territory.
Carlos Triunfel pops out to second baseman Howard Kendrick on the infield fly rule.
Trayvon Robinson singles on a ground ball to right fielder Kole Calhoun.   Jesus Montero to 3rd.    Michael Saunders to 2nd.
Trayvon Robinson grounds into a force out, shortstop Andrew Romine to second baseman Howard Kendrick.   Jesus Montero out at 2nd.
Michael Saunders pops out to third baseman Alberto Callaspo in foul territory.
Jesus Montero singles on a soft fly ball to center fielder Peter Bourjos.   John Jaso scores.    Justin Smoak to 3rd.
Justin Smoak singles on a ground ball to left fielder Mike Trout, deflected by third baseman Alberto Callaspo.   John Jaso to 2nd.
Kyle Seager pops out to first baseman Kendrys Morales in foul territory.
Michael Saunders flies out to left fielder Kole Calhoun.
John Jaso lines out to right fielder Torii Hunter.
